msgctxt "talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.te_si>...<2.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"You have done well to find this spring.<3.pa>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (blue)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk22"
msgid ""
"You who has claimed the Spirit Orbs.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Rid the blue spirit <1.se_co>Naydra <2.re_co>of Malice.\n"
"Show me the power you hold."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (blue)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk23"
msgid ""
"By your power, the blue spirit of\n"
"Mount Lanayru, <1.se_co>Naydra<2.re_co>, has been freed\n"
"of Malice."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (blue)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "talk24"
msgid ""
"Now, at last, you must pierce the body\n"
"of <1.se_co>Naydra<2.re_co>.<3.pa> This final ritual will release\n"
"the spirit of this land."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk27"
msgid ""
"Offer <1.se_co>Dinraal's scale<2.re_co>, received from\n"
"the red spirit, to the <3.se_co>Spring of Power<4.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk28"
msgid ""
"Offer <1.se_co>Farosh's scale<2.re_co>, received from the\n"
"golden spirit, to the <3.se_co>Spring of Courage<4.re_co>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk30"
msgid "Your path has shown itself. Now go forth."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk31"
msgid "I, Goddess Hylia,<1.pa> will guide you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (blue)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk32"
msgid ""
"The blue spirit, <1.se_co>Naydra<2.re_co>, is released.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"You must now offer <3.se_co>Naydra's scale<4.re_co> to\n"
"the spring here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "talk33"
msgid ""
"Link... It appears that you have sufficient\n"
"power. You should not seek to increase\n"
"this any further."
msgstr ""

